findings.title: Owner can change tax and liquidity fees
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify tax and liquidity fees.

findings.title: Owner can change maximum transaction amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum transaction amount.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude certain addresses or transactions from paying fees.

findings.title: Owner can change marketingDivisor
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the marketing divisor, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change minimum number of tokens to add to liquidity
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify the minimum number of tokens required to add to liquidity, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can change buyBackUpperLimit
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the buyBackUpperLimit, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can change marketing address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the marketing address.

findings.title: Owner can manually buyBack
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to manually initiate a buyback process.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw contract BNB balance to marketing address
findings.description: The owner has the capability to withdraw the entire BNB balance of the contract to the marketing address.

findings.title: Owner can enable and disable buyBack
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to enable or disable the buyback feature.

findings.title: Owner can enable before and after presale modes
findings.description: The owner has privileges to enable or disable presale modes, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can lock and unlock
findings.description: The owner has privileges to lock and unlock, which could allow them to retake privileges even after ownership was renounced.
